{"tid":1170563,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行offer 一問","createTime":"2019-05-25T05:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T10:47:57.000Z","uid":118534,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"718690720def6b6505cc17aaf173dc46309e4ccb","tid":1170563,"uid":118534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"大家點睇中小型銀行既前景 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟18fg 係一間細銀行做緊trainee 近日收到兩個offer <br />\n<br />\n一間係local bank mt offer （人工高依家25% 不過係做retail唔係corp）<br />\n另一間係list com 既finance dept (人工差唔多）<br />\n<br />\nlist com 個offer就應該唔會考慮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該留係依家間細行繼續發展儲多段時間經驗再報其他大bank 既perm 定係轉去其他bank mt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0ab0856170cbe76603b82cf4ec71f98b2287b5","tid":1170563,"uid":96662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"retail狗也不屌<br />\n利申做過retail, 衣家做緊corp"},{"pid":"0564002a8fa71cf6d2bafb1ca1fd7b139d7cdaa5","tid":1170563,"uid":118534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba0ab0856170cbe76603b82cf4ec71f98b2287b5","tid":1170563,"uid":96662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"retail狗也不屌<br />\n利申做過retail, 衣家做緊corp"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"retail 轉corp 好似好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 係咪graduate program 既retail 係咪都有伏味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲interview 果陣個dept head 話retail front line 同support line 都會去attach，所以未必淨係做前線"},{"pid":"ab3f65d7c9fe80b2f76b1893aebd2575898d51fd","tid":1170563,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"